1:1: COMMENT NOTE
1:7: STR_LIT "
    斯篇專作「九章算術」算理之驗證。
    考其加減乘除、所餘幾何之法，
    以驗編譯器於算術運算、變數易值之全功。
"
7:1: HERE_ARE i have
7:8: NUMBER_LIT 2
7:10: VAR_TYPE num
7:15: SAID called
7:22: NUMBER_LIT 10
7:26: SAID called
7:33: NUMBER_LIT 3
7:36: NAME_IT name it
7:44: IDENT '甲'
7:48: SAID called
7:55: IDENT '乙'
8:1: HERE_ARE i have
8:8: NUMBER_LIT 2
8:10: VAR_TYPE str
8:15: SAID called
8:22: STR_LIT "今有甲數為"
8:33: SAID called
8:40: IDENT '甲'
8:45: PRINT print
9:1: HERE_ARE i have
9:8: NUMBER_LIT 2
9:10: VAR_TYPE str
9:15: SAID called
9:22: STR_LIT "又有乙數為"
9:33: SAID called
9:40: IDENT '乙'
9:45: PRINT print
11:1: EXP_MATH +
11:5: IDENT '甲'
11:9: <-
11:12: IDENT '乙'
11:17: NAME_IT name it
11:25: IDENT '和'
11:62: COMMENT NOTE
11:67: STR_LIT " 和 = 乙 + 甲  "
12:1: HERE_ARE i have
12:8: NUMBER_LIT 2
12:10: VAR_TYPE str
12:15: SAID called
12:22: STR_LIT "甲乙相并，厥和乃為"
12:37: SAID called
12:44: IDENT '和'
12:49: PRINT print
14:1: EXP_MATH -
14:5: IDENT '甲'
14:9: ->
14:12: IDENT '乙'
14:17: NAME_IT name it
14:25: IDENT '差'
14:62: COMMENT NOTE
14:67: STR_LIT " 差 = 甲 - 乙  "
15:1: HERE_ARE i have
15:8: NUMBER_LIT 2
15:10: VAR_TYPE str
15:15: SAID called
15:22: STR_LIT "以乙損甲，其差為"
15:36: SAID called
15:43: IDENT '差'
15:48: PRINT print
17:1: EXP_MATH -
17:5: IDENT '甲'
17:9: <-
17:12: IDENT '乙'
17:17: NAME_IT name it
17:25: IDENT '反差'
17:61: COMMENT NOTE
17:66: STR_LIT " 反差 = 乙 - 甲 "
18:1: HERE_ARE i have
18:8: NUMBER_LIT 2
18:10: VAR_TYPE str
18:15: SAID called
18:22: STR_LIT "以甲損乙，反得其差為"
18:38: SAID called
18:45: IDENT '反差'
18:51: PRINT print
20:1: EXP_MATH *
20:5: IDENT '甲'
20:9: ->
20:12: IDENT '乙'
20:17: NAME_IT name it
20:25: IDENT '積'
20:62: COMMENT NOTE
20:67: STR_LIT " 積 = 甲 x 乙 "
21:1: HERE_ARE i have
21:8: NUMBER_LIT 2
21:10: VAR_TYPE str
21:15: SAID called
21:22: STR_LIT "甲乙相乘，步其積為"
21:37: SAID called
21:44: IDENT '積'
21:49: PRINT print
23:1: EXP_MATH /
23:5: IDENT '甲'
23:9: ->
23:12: IDENT '乙'
23:17: NAME_IT name it
23:25: IDENT '商'
23:62: COMMENT NOTE
23:67: STR_LIT " 商 = 甲 ÷ 乙 "
24:1: EXP_MATH /
24:5: IDENT '甲'
24:9: ->
24:12: IDENT '乙'
24:17: EXP_MATH_OP %
24:22: NAME_IT name it
24:30: IDENT '餘'
24:57: COMMENT NOTE
24:62: STR_LIT " 餘 = 甲 % 乙 "
25:1: HERE_ARE i have
25:8: NUMBER_LIT 4
25:10: VAR_TYPE str
25:15: SAID called
25:22: STR_LIT "以乙除甲，得商"
25:35: SAID called
25:42: IDENT '商'
25:47: SAID called
25:54: STR_LIT "，不盡者為"
25:65: SAID called
25:72: IDENT '餘'
25:77: PRINT print
27:1: EXP_MATH +
27:5: IDENT '甲'
27:9: <-
27:12: NUMBER_LIT 1
27:15: PAST prev
27:20: IDENT '甲'
27:24: TOPIC topic
27:31: SET set
27:35: ITS its
27:39: IS_THUS is thus
27:74: COMMENT NOTE
27:79: STR_LIT " 甲 = 1 + 甲 "
28:1: HERE_ARE i have
28:8: NUMBER_LIT 2
28:10: VAR_TYPE str
28:15: SAID called
28:22: STR_LIT "甲益一算，厥數乃為"
28:37: SAID called
28:44: IDENT '甲'
28:49: PRINT print
30:1: EXP_MATH -
